code: @Override public boolean matches(Class<?> clazz) {     return (this.checkInherited ? AnnotatedElementUtils.hasAnnotation(clazz, this.annotationType) : clazz.isAnnotationPresent(this.annotationType)). }

@Override public boolean equals(Object other) {     if (this == other) {         return true.     }     if (!(other instanceof AnnotationClassFilter)) {         return false.     }     AnnotationClassFilter otherCf = (AnnotationClassFilter) other.     return (this.annotationType.equals(otherCf.annotationType) && this.checkInherited == otherCf.checkInherited). }
@Override public String toString() {     return getClass().getName() + ": " + this.annotationType. }
